# 📝 To-Do List — Project 1

A command-line To-Do List application built with Python.
Developed as part of the DecodeLabs Python Internship (Batch 2026).

---

## 🚀 What It Does

- Add tasks to your list
- View all saved tasks
- Tasks are saved to a file — they don't disappear after closing!
- Handles invalid input gracefully

---

## 💡 Concepts Used

- Python Lists (`append`)
- `while` loop
- `if / elif / else`
- File Handling (`open`, `read`, `write`)
- `try / except` for error handling

---

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
python todolist.py
```

---

## 📸 Sample Output
Welcome to My to do list!

ADD task
View Tasks
Quit

Enter Your choice 1/2/3: 1

Enter your task: Finish Python assignment

Task Added!

Enter Your choice 1/2/3: 2

Finish Python assignment

Enter Your choice 1/2/3: 3

Goodbye!


---

